---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="关于我们 - AffDirs | 值得信赖的开发者导航">
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-white to-blue-50" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/AboutPage">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-20">
        
        <div class="text-center space-y-6">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight" itemprop="headline">
            让每一次搜索都<span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600">值得信赖</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            AffDirs 致力于在信息过载的时代，为独立开发者和创作者提供一道“过滤器”。
            <br class="hidden md:block" />
            只收录真正提升效率的优质工具，拒绝无效信息。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-xl shadow-blue-900/5 border border-slate-100 relative overflow-hidden" itemprop="mainEntity" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-4 -mr-4 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-transparent rounded-full opacity-50 blur-2xl"></div>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8 md:gap-10 relative z-10">
            <div class="shrink-0 relative">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full p-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-500">
                <div class="w-full h-full rounded-full bg-white p-1 overflow-hidden">
                  <img src="https://pub-89da898cfdba40ebb5e6144637a364cd.r2.dev/unnamed.jpg" alt="zhuima" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-full" itemprop="image" />
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-1 right-1 bg-green-500 text-white text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border-2 border-white shadow-sm">
                Owner
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center md:text-left flex-1 space-y-4">
              <div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 flex items-center justify-center md:justify-start gap-2">
                  Hi, 我是 <span itemprop="name" class="text-blue-600">zhuima</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-500 font-medium mt-1" itemprop="jobTitle">独立开发者 / 全栈工程师</p>
              </div>
              
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                作为一名天天和代码打交道的开发者，我深知“找工具”的痛苦：搜索结果充斥着广告、SEO 垃圾站和过时的教程。
              </p>
              <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                创建 <strong>AffDirs</strong> 的初衷很简单：我希望建立一个<span class="font-semibold text-slate-900">“经过人工验证的”</span>资源库。这里的每一个链接，都是我自己开发过程中觉得好用、并愿意推荐给朋友的宝藏。
              </p>

              <div class="pt-2 flex justify-center md:justify-start gap-4">
                <a href="https://github.com/zhuima" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-800 transition shadow-lg shadow-slate-900/20">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 0C4.477 0 0 4.484 0 10.017c0 4.425 2.865 8.18 6.839 9.504.5.092.682-.217.682-.483 0-.237-.008-.868-.013-1.703-2.782.605-3.369-1.343-3.369-1.343-.454-1.158-1.11-1.466-1.11-1.466-.908-.62.069-.608.069-.608 1.003.07 1.531 1.032 1.531 1.032.892 1.53 2.341 1.088 2.91.832.092-.647.35-1.088.636-1.338-2.22-.253-4.555-1.113-4.555-4.951 0-1.093.39-1.988 1.029-2.688-.103-.253-.446-1.272.098-2.65 0 0 .84-.27 2.75 1.026A9.564 9.564 0 0110 4.844c.85.004 1.705.115 2.504.337 1.909-1.296 2.747-1.027 2.747-1.027.546 1.379.203 2.398.1 2.651.64.7 1.028 1.595 1.028 2.688 0 3.848-2.339 4.695-4.566 4.942.359.31.678.921.678 1.856 0 1.338-.012 2.419-.012 2.747 0 .268.18.58.688.482A10.019 10.019 0 0020 10.017C20 4.484 15.522 0 10 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                  <span>GitHub</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center text-slate-900 mb-10">我们的收录标准</h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-2xl">🔍</div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">人工亲测</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                拒绝爬虫抓取的垃圾数据。收录的每一个工具，我都进行过基础功能测试，确保真实可用。
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-2xl">🛡️</div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">拒绝流氓</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                对用户体验零容忍。弹窗过多、强制捆绑下载或存在安全风险的站点，主要功能再强也不予收录。
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 text-2xl">⚖️</div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-2">客观中立</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                如果文章包含推广链接，我会明确标注。但这绝不影响评价维度，"好用"是唯一的上榜理由。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>


      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>